Enum Class cLoggingBase.eLogLevel

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<cLoggingBase.eLogLevel>
Logging.cLoggingBase.eLogLevel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<cLoggingBase.eLogLevel>, Constable
Enclosing class:
cLoggingBase
public static enum cLoggingBase.eLogLevel extends Enum<cLoggingBase.eLogLevel>
Enumeration of available logging levels. Levels are ordered from lowest to highest priority. When a log level is set, all messages at that level and lower will be logged.
